{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And though I constantly was more careful with war events-- now when the Hungarian Fascists took over, I could see the danger because they were killing people in front of me.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were killing people not moving fast enough in the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were killing them then they stepped out of the road.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the real danger was visible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, I also knew that they were killing people by taking whole apartment houses to the Danube River and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I knew that because we rescued a few people who survived there and took them in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they told us what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was fully aware at the very end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say only the last two months, I knew they were out to kill us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But previously I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tell me about liberation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liberation was a-- a very [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] interesting event.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Almost anti-climactic because we knew that the Russian army's moving closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to move on the street, our team.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had many losses as a result of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had to be on the street to pick up wounded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we also picked up the dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was our responsibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for just three days prior to liberation, I met a policeman who eventually were pressed into military service in-- a few blocks away from us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I asked him, how is the situation?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said this, they just beat me out of the [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Abbazia ?] coffeehouse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It almost sounded like a-- a-- a brawl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was already less than two kilometers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If I would make a local comparison, this was as far from me as I can come from here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I knew that they were very close.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
